      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS, both of which have been meticulously calibrated for optimal volumetric efficiency. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, the rod bearings have been addressed and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014critical preventative measures for this chassis. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a variable M differential lock that ensures linear power delivery. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, with bushings and dampers providing the communicative, high-fidelity feedback expected of a pristine M-division product. This vehicle is free of fluid leaks, diagnostic codes, or deferred maintenance, representing a rare opportunity for the technical purist.",
